Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.17,0:00:03.98,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Friendship! Romance! Mystery!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.11,0:00:05.75,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We try our best because we've made those promises!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.23,0:00:07.96,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,An ordinary train station with an unusual case.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.94,0:00:09.45,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,A mere piece of paper's distance separates good and evil!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.74,0:00:11.34,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Perceiving the one and only truth...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.34,0:00:13.22,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The appearance of a child and the intellect of an adult...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.22,0:00:15.10,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,His name is: Detective Conan!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.98,0:01:56.44,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Geez.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.44,0:02:00.23,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's because you're always drinking juice that you have to go to the restroom so often.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.94,0:02:02.90,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But it was really good, wasn't it, Uncle?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.57,0:02:06.28,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If only Ran{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-neechan{\r} could've come...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.57,0:02:10.70,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It couldn't be helped since she had some club activity suddenly come up.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.70,0:02:12.54,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,By the way, how about this?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.91,0:02:14.91,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Let's get some good ramen before going back!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.16,0:02:17.79,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,More food?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.33,0:02:22.96,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Well, I couldn't enjoy the French cuisine because my back was sore from the seats.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.26,0:02:25.21,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So, let's take a detour!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.34,0:02:28.97,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Next stop is Nishi-Sumida.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.97,0:02:30.26,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Nishi-Sumida.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.94,0:02:42.65,Dialogue Top,,0,0,0,,HIDDEN CIRCUMSTANCES OF THE FALLING INCIDENT
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.36,0:02:49.82,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The train is now approaching the station.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.33,0:03:00.88,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ramen!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.88,0:03:02.13,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Let's go, Conan.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.13,0:03:03.88,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'll order the salty flavor.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.88,0:03:05.13,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,How about you?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.63,0:03:08.88,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey, hey, are you really going, Uncle?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.05,0:03:10.05,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You bastard!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.64,0:03:20.02,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Geez, can't they just get along?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.48,0:03:22.31,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Knock it off, stop the fighting!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.57,0:03:30.70,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Didn't you hear me?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.70,0:03:31.66,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I said knock it off!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.67,0:04:24.29,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh, Inspector Gotou.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.29,0:04:25.25,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We've been waiting for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.00,0:04:28.00,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Something wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.68,0:04:34.51,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Mouri?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.43,0:04:37.68,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You're Mouri{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.68,0:04:38.97,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The famous detective?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.14,0:04:41.27,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Is that true?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.69,0:04:43.51,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You got it...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.15,0:04:47.40,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm Gotou from the Nishi-Sumida Police Station.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.40,0:04:49.78,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I heard about you a long time ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.78,0:04:52.90,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But I never thought I'd run into you here!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.90,0:04:54.41,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Such a joy!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.41,0:04:58.58,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It just so happens that he witnessed the fight that led to this incident.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.20,0:05:04.83,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah, I suppose that's the case...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.29,0:05:07.50,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh, that's great then!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.50,0:05:10.55,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It'll be a pleasure to have Mouri{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} working on this case!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.17,0:05:13.59,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ah, no, the pleasure's mine.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.59,0:05:17.18,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Just let me, Mouri Kogoro, take care of this case.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.14,0:05:20.72,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey, hey...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.14,0:05:23.18,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So, we know the victim's identity?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.69,0:05:24.69,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yes, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.69,0:05:27.31,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Furuta Keisuke{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}, age 41.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.31,0:05:29.52,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He works at a nearby company.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.52,0:05:33.53,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He usually takes this express train to work, and was likely on his way home.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.78,0:05:37.32,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The cause of death is a fracture to his skull due to the impact.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.99,0:05:42.16,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The one who got into a fight with him was Sugimoto Hideki{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}, age 27.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.66,0:05:44.91,Character Card,,0,0,0,,Sugimoto Hideki (27)
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.91,0:05:44.91,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,A company employee from the city.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.83,0:05:48.00,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm Gotou from Nishi-Sumida.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.00,0:05:50.88,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I have a few questions to ask you.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.17,0:05:53.84,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's too loud here.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.05,0:05:57.80,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If that's the case, please feel free to use our employee break room.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.43,0:05:59.60,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Moriya{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.60,0:06:01.35,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yes, right this way.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.72,0:06:03.68,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Thanks for the help.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.98,0:06:09.52,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What's with this wound?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.32,0:06:18.98,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I was on my way home today after treating a customer to dinner.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.24,0:06:28.37,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I got up to use the restroom, and left my bag on the rack while I was in there.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.67,0:06:40.39,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I stayed in there a while due to an upset stomach, and when I returned my bag was missing.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.93,0:06:42.89,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh, and then?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.89,0:06:45.43,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Then, when we reached the station...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.02,0:06:48.80,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I saw that guy leaving with my bag.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.15,0:06:50.06,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hold it!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.40,0:06:52.40,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What are you doing with my bag?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.86,0:06:54.07,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Who are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.08,0:06:56.44,Character Card,,0,0,0,,Furuta Keisuke (42)\NCompany Employee
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.53,0:06:56.44,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What are you talking about?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.03,0:07:00.16,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But he refused to return it.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.16,0:07:02.11,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And that's what you two fought over?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.62,0:07:03.91,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yes...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.91,0:07:06.29,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Then, when I tried to take my bag back...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.58,0:07:08.87,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The strap broke...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.59,0:07:22.60,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And unfortunately, they hadn't yet put the safety fence around the construction site.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.47,0:07:27.60,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Then, you'd never met Furuta{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} before, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.98,0:07:30.27,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.27,0:07:31.35,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I hadn't.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.94,0:07:35.94,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What do you think, Mouri{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.40,0:07:38.74,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's truly a shame.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.74,0:07:42.57,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If Furuta{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} had never taken Sugimoto{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}'s bag in the first place...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.16,0:07:46.04,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,None of this would've happened.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.87,0:07:48.91,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Uhm...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.71,0:07:53.33,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Did Furuta{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} really take that bag?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.21,0:07:55.92,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What do you mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.30,0:07:58.92,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Could he have mistaken it for lost luggage?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.18,0:08:01.38,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Lost luggage?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.51,0:08:02.22,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.84,0:08:06.51,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He's brought lost items to us before.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.10,0:08:11.89,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's rare to find kind people like him nowadays, and everyone here speaks highly of him...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.44,0:08:15.77,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I really don't think he's the kind of person who would do this.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.53,0:08:17.78,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Is that true?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.15,0:08:22.36,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Mouri{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.99,0:08:26.78,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If what you've said is true...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.79,0:08:30.37,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Then the victim may have already tried to determine the identity of the owner.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.16,0:08:33.54,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh, go confirm this with the passengers.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.54,0:08:34.96,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Right, understood.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.34,0:08:38.59,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Inspector...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.05,0:08:41.88,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Now, now, please hold on, Sugimoto{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.88,0:08:44.01,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We have to wait for testimony from witnesses first.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.64,0:08:54.60,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's just as the station worker said.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.94,0:08:59.40,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Apparently, Furuta{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} attempted to find the bag's owner before getting out.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.28,0:09:02.65,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Are you sure?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.03,0:09:07.53,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,There are passengers who remember you.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.53,0:09:11.66,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,According to them, Furuta{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} had gotten on the train after Sugimoto{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} went to the restroom.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.25,0:09:16.00,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,In other words, Sugimoto{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} left his bag on the rack and went to the restroom.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.79,0:09:22.59,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Afterwards, Furuta{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} got on the train and took the bag thinking that someone had forgotten it.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.05,0:09:28.10,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,However, Sugimoto{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} didn't know this, and thought that his bag had been stolen.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.56,0:09:33.64,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You then found Furuta{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} among the other passengers with your bag, and tried to take it back.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.65,0:09:38.27,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,From Furuta{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}'s point of view, after confirming that the owner was not around...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.69,0:09:42.28,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It wouldn't be feasible to believe that someone suddenly appeared to claim it.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.49,0:09:45.82,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Instead, with his strong sense of righteousness...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.82,0:09:48.78,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He got into a struggle while attempting to protect the bag.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.53,0:09:52.79,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And ended up dying in an unfortunate accident, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.21,0:09:54.79,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Noway...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.25,0:09:58.38,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And what about you, Sugimoto{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.38,0:10:01.80,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Was it really necessary to get in a fight over such a thing?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.92,0:10:04.84,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I was reckless...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.84,0:10:08.30,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He intended to take it to the lost & found out of kindness.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.30,0:10:11.22,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But ended up dying in such a resentful way.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.06,0:10:15.77,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,In any case, you can have this back.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.28,0:10:25.40,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's gone!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.82,0:10:27.91,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What seems to be the problem?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.41,0:10:29.99,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The receipt is gone.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.33,0:10:31.74,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Receipt?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.74,0:10:34.00,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The receipt from when I treated that customer to dinner.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.37,0:10:37.00,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It was with the rest of the money in here...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.21,0:10:39.25,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But now it's all gone.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.04,0:10:43.37,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Are you sure they aren't in your pocket?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.59,0:10:45.80,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No, I clearly remember putting it in my wallet.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.34,0:10:47.80,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Not good...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.80,0:10:50.75,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Maybe they fell on the station floor during the fight?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.47,0:10:52.26,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Saitou{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.02,0:10:54.06,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'll go check.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.23,0:11:01.23,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,How'd it go?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.48,0:11:02.27,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Well...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.69,0:11:05.74,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It seems that it did not fall out.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.74,0:11:06.90,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Also, Inspector...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.49,0:11:10.16,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I've retrieved Furuta{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}'s belongings.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.99,0:11:14.36,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,A multi-course dinner in Sasayama?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.45,0:11:19.78,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Inspector, may I see that for a moment?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.04,0:11:23.09,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ah, here you go.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.09,0:11:24.50,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Excuse me for a moment.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.92,0:11:26.63,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I knew it!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.63,0:11:29.22,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,This is my missing receipt!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.72,0:11:32.18,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,See, "Sugimoto Hideki{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-sama{\r}."
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.18,0:11:35.14,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And the amount charged is the same, 25,000 yen.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.06,0:11:40.60,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But why was it in Furuta{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}'s pocket?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.69,0:11:48.28,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Uhm, actually...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.07,0:11:51.99,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It only happened once, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.99,0:11:57.70,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,There was an incident wherein money was missing from an item Furuta{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} turned in.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.08,0:11:59.12,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What was that?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.71,0:12:02.67,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Furuta{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} was also suspected at that time, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.59,0:12:07.09,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,A thief usually wouldn't turn in the rest of the items.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.17,0:12:10.83,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I see, so that's what happened.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.68,0:12:16.85,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Furuta{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} could have stolen the money while pretending to just turn the bag in.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.85,0:12:19.23,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's a common form of theft.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.56,0:12:21.85,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Form of theft?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.85,0:12:24.23,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's why he refused to return the bag.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.23,0:12:27.73,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It would expose his crime if he had.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.99,0:12:30.44,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Is that so?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.32,0:12:35.24,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But to think it ended like that for Furuta{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.24,0:12:36.70,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I don't believe it.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.04,0:12:38.95,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Sugimoto{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.95,0:12:40.20,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.79,0:12:44.83,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Just in case, please check to see if anything else is missing.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.85,0:12:59.97,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.35,0:13:01.56,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Is that so?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.64,0:13:02.98,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Then, for the time being...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.60,0:13:05.76,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Would you mind filling this out?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.02,0:13:06.61,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.15,0:13:13.65,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Uhm, can I borrow a pen?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.82,0:13:16.91,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh, my apologies, I forgot about that.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.20,0:13:20.62,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ah, excuse me.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.35,0:13:41.47,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You bastard!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.48,0:13:46.69,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,As I thought...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.62,0:14:01.24,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I see, so that's how it happened.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.12,0:14:03.50,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I've figured it out...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.58,0:14:06.00,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The true secret behind this accident!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.71,0:14:16.55,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Geez, what's so important that it can't wait?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.89,0:14:20.85,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Where'd that brat Conan go?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.85,0:14:23.10,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,After calling me all the way over here...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.53,0:14:36.36,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Leave it to me, Uncle.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.37,0:14:40.37,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,All right, we're all good.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.45,0:14:44.20,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Inspector Gotou.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.33,0:14:46.29,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.62,0:14:50.41,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Mouri{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} wants all of us to come to the boarding area.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.30,0:14:52.38,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Boarding area?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.51,0:14:56.76,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What's going on, Mouri{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.01,0:14:59.89,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,This pose...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.14,0:15:03.22,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's the renowned Sleeping Kogoro!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.73,0:15:07.23,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But, Inspector!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.19,0:15:09.60,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ah, Mouri{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.61,0:15:14.32,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,This case was just an accident due to a luggage misunderstanding.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.57,0:15:17.32,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's incorrect, Inspector Gotou.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.91,0:15:20.82,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What do you mean by that?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.08,0:15:23.41,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'll explain it to you now.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.41,0:15:28.87,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,First, let us first review Sugimoto{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}'s testimony again.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.37,0:15:34.63,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If I recall, after Sugimoto{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} returned from the restroom, he noticed his bag was missing...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.63,0:15:38.42,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And then he saw Furuta{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} with it in the station, so he quickly left the train.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.01,0:15:40.47,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Is that correct?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.47,0:15:42.35,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yes, there's no mistake.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.64,0:15:49.64,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,However, when we saw it happen, Sugimoto{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} jumped out from behind the vending machine.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.94,0:15:52.36,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Is there something wrong with that?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.44,0:15:55.19,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Don't you find it odd?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.44,0:16:01.16,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Why would he be there if he had just come off of the train?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.83,0:16:06.12,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I guess he came from the complete opposite direction.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.99,0:16:10.74,Dialogue Top,,0,0,0,,Construction Area\NConstruction Materials\NFuruta\N1st Car\NVending Machine\NSugi-moto\NPlatform
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.33,0:16:08.08,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I see!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.83,0:16:10.75,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Now that I think about it...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.08,0:16:13.92,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It doesn't make any sense to appear from here.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.50,0:16:18.51,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But why would Sugimoto{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} do that?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.97,0:16:20.72,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He was waiting...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.97,0:16:23.72,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,For Furuta{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} to steal the money.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.81,0:16:26.22,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What was that?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.22,0:16:28.35,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No way, you just made that up!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.52,0:16:36.40,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Sugimoto{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} most likely figured that Furuta{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} would steal the money while pretending to turn in the lost bag.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.73,0:16:41.86,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's why he purposely put his receipt in his wallet.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.20,0:16:51.75,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If the receipt is found on Furuta{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}, it would expose his thievery and make taking the bag back easy.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.75,0:16:53.12,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Stop pushing your claims!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.83,0:16:54.92,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Then...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.92,0:16:55.79,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.79,0:16:59.71,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,To allow Furuta{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} to steal the money...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.72,0:17:04.14,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Sugimoto{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} purposely left the bag on the rack when he went to the restroom.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.55,0:17:08.89,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But there were other passengers there.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.89,0:17:11.98,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,How would Furuta{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} know it was a lost bag?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.60,0:17:14.19,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It was the cell phone.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.86,0:17:17.27,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Cell phone?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.61,0:17:19.53,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Didn't you notice?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.53,0:17:21.99,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The cell phone was in the bag.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.74,0:17:26.99,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The cell phone he took out probably had an unanswered call.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.62,0:17:38.13,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Just before the train pulled into the station, Sugimoto{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} called that cell phone with another one from the restroom.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.06,0:17:50.47,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And no one ended up answering the phone.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.47,0:17:53.10,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Therefore it seemed to be a lost bag.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.31,0:17:54.89,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.90,0:17:56.81,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,As expected of Sleeping Kogoro.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.40,0:18:01.11,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Furuta{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} went and hid behind the construction zone.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.11,0:18:05.57,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And after watching him steal the money out of the bag from the vending machine, Sugimoto{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.57,0:18:10.54,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Confronted Furuta{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} and pushed him into the construction zone.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.54,0:18:13.41,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He was then knocked to the ground.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.38,0:18:23.29,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Of course, he had laid the warning sign face down on the ground.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.05,0:18:26.26,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He had also cut the rope.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.10,0:18:34.52,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Then all he had to do was take the bag from the fallen victim.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.52,0:18:40.94,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If Furuta{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} didn't want the bag to be taken, he'd reach for the straps, which had already been weakened.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.07,0:18:46.20,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,After losing his balance, Furuta{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} would fall off the edge.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.86,0:18:50.66,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Excuse me, but I need to check the straps of your bag.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.25,0:18:54.83,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Inspector!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.12,0:18:56.16,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.17,0:18:58.04,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,This case wasn't an accident.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.17,0:19:01.21,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It was a premeditated murder disguised as an accidental death.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.67,0:19:04.59,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What is this?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.59,0:19:06.22,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,This is all just conjecture.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.43,0:19:07.63,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Don't you see?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.64,0:19:11.80,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That guy was hanging onto my bag with all of his strength.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.81,0:19:15.43,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Forcing him to fall while we were arguing...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.43,0:19:17.94,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,How could I possibly do something like that?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.65,0:19:20.48,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You could easily manage it...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.82,0:19:26.49,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,By using the ballpoint pen in the pocket of your coat.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.57,0:19:28.61,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ballpoint pen?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.70,0:19:33.66,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,While fighting behind the construction area...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.66,0:19:37.25,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You stabbed Furuta{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} with that ballpoint pen.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.84,0:19:48.97,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And then, you pushed him backward as he was getting up.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.27,0:19:58.56,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,They're still there, you know.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.56,0:20:03.77,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The marks you made on Furuta{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}'s right hand with your ballpoint pen.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.23,0:20:06.15,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What do you say to that?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.74,0:20:07.65,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Sugimoto{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.63,0:20:25.09,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Sugimoto{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.88,0:20:27.76,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I couldn't forgive that guy!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.51,0:20:29.97,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Because he took...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.63,0:20:32.29,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,My girlfriend's life!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.56,0:20:37.68,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Half a year ago...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.27,0:20:41.19,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,When she was crossing the street...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.19,0:20:43.06,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He was speeding and ran her over!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.24,0:21:00.58,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We had decided to get married soon...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.42,0:21:05.75,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Since there were no other witnesses...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.75,0:21:09.63,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,They believed his testimony that she suddenly jumped into the street.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.22,0:21:11.72,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That bastard escaped punishment!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.47,0:21:13.55,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,How...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.26,0:21:16.05,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,How could he...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.72,0:21:20.68,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So you wanted to kill Furuta{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.68,0:21:22.68,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And decided to set up this trap?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.02,0:21:23.94,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That guy...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.73,0:21:25.90,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's all his fault!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.52,0:21:28.78,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,How was I supposed to forgive that!?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.99,0:23:04.25,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,All right, it's ready to eat!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.17,0:23:09.00,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Geez, Dad...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:09.00,0:23:14.76,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Even if the ramen place was closed, you didn't have to buy cup ramen to eat.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.76,0:23:16.01,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Right, Conan{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.84,0:23:19.97,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's not a big deal.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:19.97,0:23:22.14,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I really like this!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.73,0:23:34.90,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Delicious!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.99,0:23:38.36,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'll have another!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:38.36,0:23:39.41,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You're gonna get fat.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:40.57,0:23:45.33,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Well, for Uncle, this kind of food suits him better than that French cuisine.
